name: Rex Software
description: Rex Software makes real estate CRM software that works everywhere you do.
entry-instructions: There is a black "Rex Software" sign next to the front door.
transport:
Street parking can be pretty tricky, so it would be a good idea to allow extra time if driving. There is 2 hour free parking nearby at Gasworks.

If you choose public transport, the venue is close to the Teneriffe Ferry Terminal and buses. Front door will be open for the event.
